high_descs: Walk forward and turn left to face the counter to the right of the stove.
Pick up the knife on the counter.
Turn around to face the lettuce on the white table.
Cut the lettuce on the table into slices.
Turn right and walk forward to face the sink.
Place the knife in the sink.
Turn around and cross the room to face the lettuce on the white table.
Pick up a slice of lettuce on the white table.
Turn right and walk forward to face the fridge.
Cool the lettuce slice in the fridge and remove it.
Turn right and walk forward to face the sink.
Place the lettuce slice on the edge of the sink.

Pick up a slice of lettuce.
Go across the room to the fridge.
Chill the slice of lettuce in the fridge and then pick it back up.
Turn right and go to the sink.
Put the slice of lettuce on the counter in front of the left sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled slice of lettuce on the counter in front of the sink.
